               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary><p>The <title xml:lang="ta">Nīticāram</title>, “The gist of moral teachings”, a collection moral or didactic stanzas. An incomplete copy (the text stops short in U2, f49v4) in 74 stanzas, with gaps. Each stanza is followed by its commentary.</p>
<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (October 2020 and March 2022).</p> <p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p> </summary>
                  
